item.description: Sha-booooooom I lived in Karnal. I moved to Hyderabad. I now live in West Lafayette. I obssess on Elon Musk and Iron Man. I don’t like to write code but I have to. I can do data and more. I was Openlab Summer Intern at CERN. I’m not anymore but that is still cool. I have a more detailed resume if you’re into that sort of thing.
